These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, apricot
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is not the person who likes apricot##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | apricot   | brown  |
| Sport   | fishing | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, weightlifting
House: futuristic, art-deco
1. the futuristic house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
2. the futuristic house is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | ice-hockey | weightlifting      |
| Pet    | futuristic  | art-deco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
City: prague, marseilles
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, collecting
1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person traveling to prague##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | marseilles  | prague    |
| Sport   | puzzles | collecting |

