.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, car
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, dog
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the car is not the owner of the guinea-pig##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Music-Genre   | car  | skateboard      |
| Nationality   | dog | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
