There 2 different types of food: kale, cauliflower
1. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
2. the gothic-revival house is not the person eating cauliflower##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | gothic-revival | art-deco |
| Pet   | kale       | cauliflower       |

